  "stemHtml": "<p>For pre-flight planning purposes what is the required block fuel for an IFR flight with a turbine engine jet aircraft? Assume the Basic Fuel Scheme WITHOUT variations applies.</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Taxi fuel ( including APU usage):</td><td>150 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Fuel for the climb to cruise level:</td><td>1600 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Cruise distance to destination:</td><td>570 NAM</td></tr><tr><td>Cruise fuel consumption:</td><td>6 kg/NAM</td></tr><tr><td>Fuel for descent to the destination:</td><td>270 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Fuel for approach & landing destination:</td><td>450 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Contingency fuel:</td><td>5% of trip</td></tr><tr><td>Fuel for alternate:</td><td>2150 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Holding fuel flow at destination & alternate:</td><td>2200 kg/h</td></tr><tr><td>Missed approach fuel at alternate:<br>Extra Fuel:<br>Discretionary Fuel:</td><td>270 kg<br>0 kg<br>0 kg</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>",
